{
  "texts": [
    "\"Turing trap\": exclusion.DTW should highlight the subjective dimension of work over the objective dimension.DTW should focus on distinctive human qualities that are \"surprising,\" \"social,\" and \"scarce.",
    "\"Promote the performance of MacIntyrean practices (e.g., digital trainers, explainers, architects, ethicists).Primacy of objective dimension (technology, efficiency, profits, etc.)",
    "over subjective dimension (knowledge, skills, habits, virtues, attitudes, flourishing, etc.)",
    "of work.Promote the accumulation of external, institutional goods (wealth, power, fame, etc.",
    ").DTW should be organized in ways that help those whose jobs are unstable, insecure, or poorly paid.DTW should foster job resilience.Governments, labor organizations, and firms engage in solidarious efforts to achieve the conditions for \"decent work."
  ]
}